<seg id="603">Motor fuel merchant</seg>
<seg id="604">To monitor motor fuels in free tax circulation and to eliminate tax evasion, a new type of tax entity was introduced: motor fuel merchant.</seg>
<seg id="605">The Slovak Republic has no a special regulation on service stations.</seg>
