<seg id="1">Frank Lloyd Wright is reported to have said once that if you tipped the world on its side, everything loose would end up in California.</seg>
<seg id="2">We've always thought that Mr. Wright underestimated California's vitality, but maybe the state's la-la factions are starting to overwhelm the forces that made it such a significant place.</seg>
